   Ohta, Kensuke; Sada, Yoshinao, Sumitomo Chem Co Ltd, Hlth \& Crop Sci Lab, Takarazuka, Hyogo, Japan.
   Ohta, Kensuke, Kyoto Univ, Grad Sch Agr, Kyoto, Japan.},
